The,Arlo,API,is,a,REST,API,that,provides,developers,access,to,events,contacts,organization,registration,and,CRM,data,stored,in,your,Arlo,platform,The,API,also,supports,a,public,API,designed,for,browser,based,web,JavaScript,widgets,mashups,as,well,as,an,Authenticated,API,for,server,based,integration,with,websites,and,CRM,software